title: BootLine
description:
Bootline is Windows application let you burn your flash drive with multiple ISO's. It uses grub4dos as universal loader. With Bootline you can install a lot of prepared ISO's such as Windows 7,8,10, Kaspersky Rescue Disk, CloneZilla Live, Ubuntu and other. This application works stable and fast. Bootline it is portable version of web service bootline.net - you can burn your multiple ISO's to flash drive online in your browser.
